	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Repro steps:&#xD;&#xA;1. Start the game with a druid and level up (Ctrl-shift-L on the character)&#xD;&#xA;2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;3. Debug Book&#xD;&#xA;Goto region &gt; Act 1 &gt; Forest &gt; Abandoned Village&#xD;&#xA;4. Kill combat&#xD;&#xA;5. Head towards the windmill up the stairs.&#xD;&#xA;6. Morph into any wildshape.&#xD;&#xA;7. Talk to Fezzerk (Goblin with great axe)" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="5833" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="The party comes across a trio of goblins who've captured a gnome and have turned to tormenting him - they've tied him to an windmill and are watching him spin around. Here, the player approaches while using wildshape (they're in animal form, so the scene unfolds in a shortened manner that quickly turns to combat)." />
